<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="card shadow-sm">
    <div class="card-body p-5">
      <h1 class="display-5 mb-4 text-center">For Venue Owners</h1>

      <p class="lead text-center mb-4">
        Get your venue on the map and attract live music fans in your area.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-4" />

      <h4 class="text-center mb-4">Claim or Add Your Venue</h4>
      <p class="text-center">
        After signing up, you can search for your venue on the app. If it's already listed, claim it as your own to manage your events. If it's not listed yet, you can add it manually.
      </p>

      <h4 class="text-center mb-4">Post Events</h4>
      <p class="text-center">
        Once your venue is approved or created, click <strong>"Add Event"</strong> to promote a live show.
      </p>


      <hr class="my-5" />

      <div class="text-center">
        <%= link_to "Sign Up as an Owner!", new_owner_registration_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
